DELANO COAL COMPANY, Inc., Libelant-Appellant, v. Barge BLUE ROCK, Her Tackle, etc., Thomas Monk, Claimant-Appellee. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. February 5, 1929. No. 185. Single & Single, of New York City (William J. Mahar, of New York City, of counsel), for appellant. William F. Purdy, of New York City, for appellee.

Before MANTON, L. HAND, and AUGUSTUS N. HAND, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decree affirmed in open court.
